To wire a CTR Power Distribution Panel to the rev Pneumatic hub, you’ll need 18 gauge red and black wire. Strip both ends of the wire, connect one end to the power of the rev Pneumatic hub, and the other end to the PCMc12vin terminals on the Power Distribution Panel.
Here is the picture to where to get power from on the PDP

image674×518 38.6 KB

I hope that information was helpful! Please keep me posted on the outcome.
